## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of data and the scope of the sources reviewed. The complexity of domestic abuse means that not all contributing factors can be fully explored in a single report. Additionally, the nuances of individual cases and cultural differences may not be fully captured. Further research is needed to explore the intersectionality of domestic abuse and its varied manifestations across different communities.